design adds a stylish touch to your home office space. The cushioned upholstery is an absolute relief for those working long work. We love how the vibrant yellow adds a fun element to the room. At the same time, the white work desk and wood panelling on the wall make your workspace look sophisticated. The book cabinet with a glass door is a great addition to keep your books and work documents well-organised. The best part? You can use this as a lounge chair or an accent chair in your living room for relaxation after work!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181005\/best-home-office-chair-with-yellow-cushion.jpg\" alt=\"Yellow home office chair with cushion adds a stylish touch\" class=\"wp-image-28705\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181005\/best-home-office-chair-with-yellow-cushion.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181005\/best-home-office-chair-with-yellow-cushion-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181005\/best-home-office-chair-with-yellow-cushion-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181005\/best-home-office-chair-with-yellow-cushion-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A yellow cushion upholstered home office chair adds a comforting vibe to your space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180939\/end-to-end-home-interior-design-solutions-for-stunning-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Use Leather Upholstery For A Luxe Home Office Chair<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Want a luxurious and elegant vibe for your home workstation? Here\u2019s the perfect setup for you! Leather upholstered home office desk chairs skillfully add a cosy vibe. They are ideal for professional meetings and catch-ups because of their corporate looks. This home office desk and chair make your home look grand and take its style quotient to an all-new level. Moreover, the wooden panelling on the wall and wooden flooring add warmth to the space. The LED backlight and table lamp complete the look and illuminate the room beautifully.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181025\/home-center-office-chair-with-leather.jpg\" alt=\"Leather upholstered desk chairs gives your home office a cosy yet corporate vibe\" class=\"wp-image-28708\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181025\/home-center-office-chair-with-leather.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181025\/home-center-office-chair-with-leather-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181025\/home-center-office-chair-with-leather-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181025\/home-center-office-chair-with-leather-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Leather upholstered chairs give your home office a luxurious and corporate look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Metal Home Office Chair To Match Your Industrial Style Home Interiors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you prefer a trendy and unconventional look, try this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/industrial-style-home-office\/\">industrial-style home office<\/a> setup. It is minimalistic, chic, and has a rugged look to it. The brick cladding accent wall gives a modern rustic feel and adds interest to the space. The wooden study desk with drawers, metal racks, and open shelf cabinets amp up the space. Simultaneously, they offer lots of storage space. The armless metal chairs with cushion padding easily blend into the setup and give you enough comfort to work long hours. Here\u2019s a great idea for working parents of young students. Use the second chair so your kid can study beside you while you work from home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01180959\/armless-metal-home-office-chair.jpg\" alt=\"Two metal home office chairs in blue and red colour\" class=\"wp-image-28704\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01180959\/armless-metal-home-office-chair.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01180959\/armless-metal-home-office-chair-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01180959\/armless-metal-home-office-chair-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01180959\/armless-metal-home-office-chair-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Sleek minimalist home office chair to suit your industrial-style home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Home Office Chair For A Simple Workstation<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend this modest and unique home desk chair to create a Scandinavian office setup at home. The rattan seater effortlessly combines functionality with quirkiness. The light woodwork desk seamlessly matches the design scheme and creates a peaceful aura. This helps keep your space and mind uncluttered, which leads to better work performance. The tall book cabinet with open shelves and drawers gives you ample storage space and helps keep your home office neat and organised.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181011\/comfortable-home-office-chair-in-light-wood.jpg\" alt=\"A light wood home office desk and chair to match your scandinavian style home office setup\" class=\"wp-image-28706\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181011\/comfortable-home-office-chair-in-light-wood.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181011\/comfortable-home-office-chair-in-light-wood-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181011\/comfortable-home-office-chair-in-light-wood-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181011\/comfortable-home-office-chair-in-light-wood-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A light wood home office chair to match your Scandinavian-style home office setup<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Complement A Tropical-Themed Home Office With A Swivel Desk Chair<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This colourful home office is a delight for people who want to add a touch of nature to their workspace. The leaf-patterned wallpaper and turf grass flooring will help create a calming workstation vibe in your home. The swivel desk chair in teal and yellow matches the colour scheme beautifully and makes moving around easier. We have also added a yellow bean bag where you can take small breaks between work. The beehive floating wall shelves provide an innovative storage and display solution without taking up any floor space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181043\/swivel-home-office-desk-chair.jpg\" alt=\"A tropical-themed home office with a swivel desk chair ideal for a small working space\" class=\"wp-image-28711\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181043\/swivel-home-office-desk-chair.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181043\/swivel-home-office-desk-chair-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181043\/swivel-home-office-desk-chair-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181043\/swivel-home-office-desk-chair-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The best home office chair for work from home that suits tropical interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Ergonomic Home Office Chair With A Corporate Feel<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for a chair which allows you to work with concentration for longer hours, this is it. This home office setup intelligently utilises the unused space beneath the staircase in your home. We have added a swivel fluid chair with breathable back mesh and adjustable lumbar support. This is the best home office chair as it creates dynamic support that keeps the body in healthy alignment. Multiple cabinets, drawers and open shelves make this corner highly useful. Even though it is a corner, the modular design and light colour scheme make the space look bright and airy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181018\/comfortable-stylish-home-office-chair.jpg\" alt=\"A workstation beneath the staircase with a home office chair features breathable back mesh and adjustable lumbar support\" class=\"wp-image-28707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181018\/comfortable-stylish-home-office-chair.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181018\/comfortable-stylish-home-office-chair-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181018\/comfortable-stylish-home-office-chair-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181018\/comfortable-stylish-home-office-chair-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A smartly designed workstation beneath the staircase with an ergonomic fluid chair<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Add A Boho Touch To Your Home Office Desk Setup<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who said home offices have to look serious and boring? A perfect home office should include corporate elements without taking away the comfort of working from home. Too much corporate vibe makes working from home seem very mechanical. Don\u2019t opt for a sluggish setup, too, as it might hinder your productivity. We suggest creating a setup that perfectly balances the two, like this cool home office. Set right beside the window; this desk enjoys ample natural light. This ensures a well-lit and positive environment to work which lets your creative juices flow. Adding a boho touch to this setup is an innovatively designed oval rattan chair with thick cushion padding. Doesn\u2019t it bring a playful vibe to the otherwise corporate home office?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181031\/rattan-home-office-chair-in-oval-shaped.jpg\" alt=\"Oval-shaped rattan home office chair set up right beside the window\" class=\"wp-image-28709\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181031\/rattan-home-office-chair-in-oval-shaped.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181031\/rattan-home-office-chair-in-oval-shaped-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181031\/rattan-home-office-chair-in-oval-shaped-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/01181031\/rattan-home-office-chair-in-oval-shaped-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A well-lit work from home setup with a smart oval-shaped rattan home office chair<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you enjoyed our selection of unique home office chair designs. Planning to add a practical home office setup in your home? Get in touch with our designers today! They will help you get the best interior solutions with 20% extra storage space and a 10-year warranty. Book a consultation today, and let\u2019s take your interior design game higher by several notches.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/home-office-design\/\">Home Office Designed By DesignCafe<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/vastu-for-home-office\/\">Vastu For Home Office<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div c